第四九六集）<br />\n<br />\n🙏祈願師父上淨下空老和尚。法體安康。正法久住。度生無量。南無阿彌陀佛！<br />\n<br />\n🙇隨喜功德分享此文。皆悉回向給文章、圖片原作者(佛友大德)和眾讀者(佛友大德)及盡虛空遍法界一切眾生。<br />\n<br />\n📢感恩南無阿彌陀佛。閱讀開智慧。分享好文。利人利己。正法流通。功德無量。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T23:16:13.000Z","msg":"阿彌陀佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50ebb538ba34c03b5c4b929a4f3df90ff5a11a5","tid":2100127,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d89b7b35001f37b2e3556725e8e87e7432c808e7","tid":2100127,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T23:13:57.000Z","msg":"念念不忘阿彌陀佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請善用起底功能 翻看其他智慧經文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"pink\">佛教是教育，不是宗教，教什麼？教我們修清淨心，教我們幸福快樂，教我們健康長壽<br />\n<br />\n過幸福美滿的人生<br />\n學佛是人生最高的享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿彌陀佛🙏🏻</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">學佛就是將佛陀的教誨落實到日常生活當中</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n小妹的學佛筆記🙏🏻還在努力學習當中🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdvWbzO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdvWbzO.png&h=b69b0f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與佛有緣的同修可以在Facebook search 淨空法師/阿彌陀佛/念佛成佛 搜索更多經文+智慧字句<br />\n許多佛菩薩都把經文的精華/重點節錄了出來<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/amituofobuddha/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Famituofobuddha%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmrKDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=7879d9d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/amituofobuddha/?ref=share</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nianAmitabha/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FnianAmitabha%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmrKDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=c8be7f21\" target=\"_blank\">https